title: Follow 2015 Colonial League girls soccer playoffs (BRACKET)
text:
Lauren Binn and her Saucon Valley teammates enter the Colonial League playoffs with the top seed. (lehighvalleylive.com file photo) By Josh Folck | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 16, 2015 1:17 PM, updated October 16, 2015 1:47 PM 
The Colonial League girls soccer playoffs will start on Tuesday. 
Saucon Valley is the top seed in the tournament. 
The semifinals will be Tuesday night at Northern Lehigh and Salisbury. The finals are scheduled for Thursday night at a site to be determined.
